 This install applies to "Road Rash" Â© 1992 Electronic Arts - 2 disks.

 This install requires WHDLoad to be in the path. It can be found in the
 WHDLoad package.

 The installed program requires 1 MB ChipMem and 1 MB OtherMem.
 It can be quit by pressing num '*' (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, NOVBRMOVE, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
	http://www.whdload.de/
 or	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and	aminet:game/patch/

 Version 2.0 (18.08.2019) done by JOTD:
 - adapted to whdload v17
 - joypad support (issue #0003626)
 - when joypad is detected, game control text is adapted. Function
   keys become joypad buttons in the game messages.
 - ability to enter some preset passwords at startup
 - ability to enter user defined password with CUSTOM tooltype   
 - arrows mapped to joystick directions (issue #0002670)
 - enter names/passwords with joypad (no need for keyboard anymore)
 - source code included
 
 Version 1.3 (2002):
 - reworked install script. Files are now in the "data" directory,
 - manual included
 - added a ton of icons
  
 Version 1.2:
 - fixed remaining disk access
 
 Version 1.1:
 - fixed delay to see the map

 Version 1.0 (1997):
 
 - Full run from HD using WHDLoad
 - Memory patch to avoid to use 32 bit fast memory
 - Password protection removed (no more protection screen)
 

CD32 controls - menu:

F1 - RW/reverse:
F2 - FF/forward: 
F3 - Blue: enter password / select bike
F4 - Green: control method 1
F5 - Yellow: control method 2

To select a letter to input, use reverse & forward. This acts like
Earok "virtual keyboard": enters the letter then performs a cursor left
To select this letter, just use joystick right.

CD32 controls - game:

P - PLAY: pause
F10 - reverse+forward: quit current game

Custom password:

The format matters: 5 chars - 2 spaces - 8 chars - 2 spaces - 5 chars
Ex: whdload roadrash.slave preload custom="00000  01420019G5  457VO"


Thanks to Marc Kelkermans for the original disks (and to the many people who sent me
original disks of other games)

