View ending sequence:
Press [F3] at the track select screen to display the password screen. Enter 11111 02881 RNLKC 5FJ7K as a password, then start the race.
Press [F10] to quit, then press Fire at the repair cost screen to view the ending sequence. After that, the game will restart at level 1 with the Diablo 1000 bike. 

Start with Diablo:
Enter 00000 REDC0 QNGM5 172SU as a password to start at level 1 with the Diablo 1000 and a large amount of money. 

Source: GameWinners.com ,  http://www.gamewinners.com 